 Example

Here are some examples of the use of poly

  --> A = [1,2,3;4,5,6;7,8,0]

  A =
   1 2 3
   4 5 6
   7 8 0

  --> p = poly(A)

  p =
      1.0000   -6.0000  -72.0000  -27.0000

  --> r = roots(p)

  r =
     12.1229
     -5.7345
     -0.3884


